{"id":282698,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-维权人士陈美佳等人在天安门被抓后押回/","date":"2013-03-07T11:01:01Z","modified":"2013-03-07T11:01:01Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士陈美佳等人在天安门被抓后押回杭州（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员钱江报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，杭州江干区维权人士陈美佳、陆吕浩，陆定耀，李少贤等十余人，躲开维稳人员的监控到北京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>点多</span><span>钟，陈美佳等在北京右安门宾馆被北京的警察叫醒，要把他们赶走。经过房主和旅客的一番抗争和交涉后，北京公安说，你们正常上访，我们不来干涉，但这地方第二天不能再住。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因国家信访局等地方等待信访的访民排成长队，陈美佳、陆吕浩、陆定耀、李少贤等人于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日上午</span><span>去天安门游玩，警察搜查时从他们的旅行袋里搜出上访材料，于是就把他们关到了天安门地区公安分局。经过一番“审查”后，又把他们送往久敬庄关押。随后杭州江干区的截访人员接蹱而至，将他们押回杭州，现陈美佳等正在被押回杭州的路上（陈美佳手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13867155073</span><span>）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另外，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日傍晚</span><span>在北京南站被杭州国保抓走的汪雪娥（杭州著名民主党人吕耿松的妻子）至今情况不明，其手机一直无法接通。同一时间在北京南站与地方截访人员交涉的维权人士梁丽婉等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>余人随后也与外界失去联系。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XxS-B9r-pV0/UThfhGQ_esI/AAAAAAAAeec/WYekzP01N-E/s1600/UserDataImageAJANW)9%5B$3A9Z_GZ9X%2560T%2560%257DN.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XxS-B9r-pV0/UThfhGQ_esI/AAAAAAAAeec/WYekzP01N-E/s320/UserDataImageAJANW)9%5B$3A9Z_GZ9X%2560T%2560%257DN.jpg\" width=\"234\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-amWV7HvyTWs/UThfiuCglCI/AAAAAAAAeek/fkEG8GjIHPk/s1600/UserDataImageOIF%257D$)ADG%2560(5UQZ)PQVIA)K_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-amWV7HvyTWs/UThfiuCglCI/AAAAAAAAeek/fkEG8GjIHPk/s320/UserDataImageOIF%257D$)ADG%2560(5UQZ)PQVIA)K_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"220\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nq1cGF4i2yU/UThfjnNWJEI/AAAAAAAAees/hqMNIwVfPZ8/s1600/UserDataImageP%257B@%257DN4N%5BT%2525@%5DHN@NG188R7R_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nq1cGF4i2yU/UThfjnNWJEI/AAAAAAAAees/hqMNIwVfPZ8/s320/UserDataImageP%257B@%257DN4N%5BT%2525@%5DHN@NG188R7R_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"233\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-rDBFbvxVRCA/UThflebeplI/AAAAAAAAee0/eQLRj-5mk-o/s1600/UserDataImagePLDN)XPJ1%2560@I9E%5B%2525T%25606@L1W_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-rDBFbvxVRCA/UThflebeplI/AAAAAAAAee0/eQLRj-5mk-o/s320/UserDataImagePLDN)XPJ1%2560@I9E%5B%2525T%25606@L1W_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"239\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-PFsKhwY26bk/UThfm_zwYeI/AAAAAAAAee8/c2_Sgncr3wM/s1600/UserDataImageZD21899T8$A0A7D61$W~U%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"191\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-PFsKhwY26bk/UThfm_zwYeI/AAAAAAAAee8/c2_Sgncr3wM/s320/UserDataImageZD21899T8$A0A7D61$W~U%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit